<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 02:21:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国支持以色列国防部长呼吁内塔尼亚胡拒绝对加沙的军事统治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article-live/u-s-backs-israeli-defense-chiefs-call-for-netanyahu-to-reject-military-rule-in-gaza/0000018f-7f05-dd4f-ab8f-ffad91770000</link><description>国防部长约夫·加兰特：不会同意军事统治加沙 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：只要哈马斯继续存在，任何其他政党都不会在加沙进行统治 ■ 战时内阁部长甘茨在与总理的争执中支持国防部长 ■ 内塔尼亚胡向 CNBC 表示：我们不同意美国反对拉法，但会做我们必须做的事</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 01:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article-live/u-s-backs-israeli-defense-chiefs-call-for-netanyahu-to-reject-military-rule-in-gaza/0000018f-7f05-dd4f-ab8f-ffad91770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长向狡猾的欺诈者内塔尼亚胡发出的信息：你应该受到指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-chiefs-message-to-netanyahu-the-artful-fraudster-youre-to-blame/0000018f-7e1f-d604-af8f-7f1f0f480000</link><description>为了确保政府能够生存到11月，这位总理再次取消了“征兵法”策略。无奈之下，国防部长约阿夫·加兰特让公众一睹最敏感的战略讨论，并向内塔尼亚胡明确表示：你最好清醒过来——而且要快</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 21:37:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-chiefs-message-to-netanyahu-the-artful-fraudster-youre-to-blame/0000018f-7e1f-d604-af8f-7f1f0f480000</guid></item><item><title>以色列通胀卷土重来，四月份物价涨幅超出预期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/inflation-is-back-as-april-prices-rise-more-than-expected/0000018f-7dcb-d430-a38f-fdefaf830000</link><description>房价一个月上涨0.95%，特拉维夫上涨2.2% ■ 以色列央行担心新一轮通胀爆发，主要是以色列地缘政治不确定性</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 20:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/inflation-is-back-as-april-prices-rise-more-than-expected/0000018f-7dcb-d430-a38f-fdefaf830000</guid></item><item><title>进军加沙还是火炬援助？以色列极右翼如何庆祝独立日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-15/ty-article/.highlight/march-to-gaza-or-torch-aid-how-israels-far-right-celebrated-independence-day/0000018f-7d60-d7f9-a5ff-fd7604220000</link><description>一些以色列人通过焚烧为加沙巴勒斯坦平民提供的援助来标志着以色列的独立。我们彼此的愿望，明年我们享受一个更快乐的假期，似乎越来越远了</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 19:58:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-15/ty-article/.highlight/march-to-gaza-or-torch-aid-how-israels-far-right-celebrated-independence-day/0000018f-7d60-d7f9-a5ff-fd7604220000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡提交甘茨的正统法案草案；甘茨说法律无关紧要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-submit-gantzs-haredi-draft-bill-gantz-says-law-is-irrelevant/0000018f-7d90-d9d6-a38f-7dfb49530000</link><description>即使以色列总理没有计划真正通过这项法律，他也可以通过阻止高等法院并防止其政府垮台来赢得急需的时间。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 19:38:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-submit-gantzs-haredi-draft-bill-gantz-says-law-is-irrelevant/0000018f-7d90-d9d6-a38f-7dfb49530000</guid></item><item><title>第一所美国大学校长宣布全面抵制以色列学术并休假</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/in-first-california-university-announces-complete-academic-boycott-of-israel/0000018f-7d38-d604-af8f-7f39cc820000</link><description>索诺玛州立大学是一所隶属于加州州立大学系统的公立文理学院，宣布不会与以色列大学建立任何伙伴关系或合作</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 18:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/in-first-california-university-announces-complete-academic-boycott-of-israel/0000018f-7d38-d604-af8f-7f39cc820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长呼吁内塔尼亚胡拒绝对加沙的军事统治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-calls-on-netanyahu-to-reject-military-rule-in-gaza/0000018f-7ced-d0aa-abbf-feeff9070000</link><description>国防部长加兰特在向内塔尼亚胡发起挑战时表示，“只有取代哈马斯的行动者才能实现哈马斯的未来”。部长们呼吁解雇他</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 17:23:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-calls-on-netanyahu-to-reject-military-rule-in-gaza/0000018f-7ced-d0aa-abbf-feeff9070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 222 天：Gallant 命令以色列国防军准备关闭约旦河西岸的半岛电视台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-222-gallant-orders-idf-to-prepare-to-shut-down-al-jazeera-in-west-bank/0000018f-7cf9-d0aa-abbf-fefb842d0001</link><description>以色列国防部长呼吁总理内塔尼亚胡公开宣布以色列不会对加沙建立军事统治 ■ 以色列官员警告埃及可能因以色列在拉法的行动而退出停战调解努力 ■ 红十字会在加沙建立野战医院 ■ 超过 60 人以色列北部遭到火箭弹袭击。真主党声称对此次发射负责 ■ 战争进入 222 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 16:11:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-222-gallant-orders-idf-to-prepare-to-shut-down-al-jazeera-in-west-bank/0000018f-7cf9-d0aa-abbf-fefb842d0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列讽刺节目再次攻击亲巴勒斯坦的美国大学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-satire-show-takes-another-jab-at-pro-palestinian-u-s-college-students/0000018f-7c5f-d604-af8f-7f5f448d0000</link><description>“Eretz Nehederet”草图强调了对抗议参与者的一些最常见的批评——即他们对冲突缺乏真正的理解，以及一些人认为整个运动特征的自恋和特权</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 15:39:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-satire-show-takes-another-jab-at-pro-palestinian-u-s-college-students/0000018f-7c5f-d604-af8f-7f5f448d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争日记：以色列士兵写下恐惧、痛苦和朋友的死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-diaries-israeli-soldiers-write-about-fear-agony-and-the-death-of-their-friends/0000018f-72f4-db28-ab8f-f3f5a77f0000</link><description>战斗与反思：自以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，许多以色列士兵一直在写个人日记。以下是其中五篇文章的摘录</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 15:01:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-diaries-israeli-soldiers-write-about-fear-agony-and-the-death-of-their-friends/0000018f-72f4-db28-ab8f-f3f5a77f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登推进以色列军售，同时抵制共和党的努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/biden-moving-forward-with-israel-arms-sales-pushing-back-against-gop-efforts/0000018f-7c57-d0b5-a7cf-7ed72c240000</link><description>此次出售可能会在国会面临前所未有的民主党反对，上个月众议员格雷戈里·米克斯表示，他将等待政府的保证，然后再签署向以色列出售 F-15 战斗机，这就是新常态。</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 14:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/biden-moving-forward-with-israel-arms-sales-pushing-back-against-gop-efforts/0000018f-7c57-d0b5-a7cf-7ed72c240000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡禁止半岛电视台，因为他只想听到他的声音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-banned-al-jazeera-because-he-wants-only-his-voice-to-be-heard/0000018f-7c0c-d0be-a7bf-fe6e68650000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府决定禁止半岛电视台及其对新闻自由的漠视并不令人意外。这是徒劳的、危险的和反民主的。但关闭不会阻止我们对加沙战争双方的报道</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 13:32:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-banned-al-jazeera-because-he-wants-only-his-voice-to-be-heard/0000018f-7c0c-d0be-a7bf-fe6e68650000</guid></item><item><title>否认、蔑视和非人化：为什么加沙战争意味着以色列现在必须承认大灾难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/denial-and-dehumanization-why-the-gaza-war-means-israel-must-now-acknowledge-the-nakba/0000018f-7bd1-d430-a38f-fff5a8300000</link><description>当内塔尼亚胡政府的部长们威胁要发生“第二次灾难”时，同时拒绝承认 1948 年第一次驱逐巴勒斯坦人，当他们抹去绿线并声称加沙没有无辜人民时，被切断与他们的联系的不仅仅是巴勒斯坦人。根源，也是以色列人</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 13:23:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/denial-and-dehumanization-why-the-gaza-war-means-israel-must-now-acknowledge-the-nakba/0000018f-7bd1-d430-a38f-fff5a8300000</guid></item><item><title>居住在德国的一名巴勒斯坦人和一名以色列人帮助加沙人建造更安全的庇护所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-israel-bombs-gaza-a-palestinian-and-an-israeli-help-gazans-build-safer-shelters/0000018f-7b7e-dd4f-ab8f-fffee6100000</link><description>居住在德国的一名加沙人和一名以色列人为流离失所的加沙人筹集了基本基础设施的捐款，并已经建造了一个营地，为数十个家庭提供住所</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 12:59:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-israel-bombs-gaza-a-palestinian-and-an-israeli-help-gazans-build-safer-shelters/0000018f-7b7e-dd4f-ab8f-fffee6100000</guid></item><item><title>尽管禁止悬挂巴勒斯坦旗帜，仍有数十人参加特拉维夫大学的 Nakba 集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/despite-ban-on-palestinian-flags-dozens-join-nakba-rally-at-tel-aviv-university/0000018f-7c15-d604-af8f-7f153f940000</link><description>相反，抗议者挥舞着西瓜形状的标语牌。几十名 Im Tirtzu 活动人士举行了反集会。特拉维夫地区警方将旗帜禁令归因于现在的“敏感时期”</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 12:04:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/despite-ban-on-palestinian-flags-dozens-join-nakba-rally-at-tel-aviv-university/0000018f-7c15-d604-af8f-7f153f940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部召见参加浩劫游行的教师</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-ministry-calls-in-teacher-after-being-photographed-at-nakba-march/0000018f-7bc4-d808-a9bf-fbd792050000</link><description>在学生和家长向学校官员施加压力要求解雇 Sabreen Msarwi 后，教育部表示将寻求澄清此事</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 11:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-ministry-calls-in-teacher-after-being-photographed-at-nakba-march/0000018f-7bc4-d808-a9bf-fbd792050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列古镇的巨型罐子让考古学家困惑不已</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/giant-jars-in-small-ancient-town-in-israel-puzzle-archaeologists/0000018f-7b7b-dd4f-ab8f-ffff331a0000</link><description>Pithoi 在青铜时代的地中海地区曾风靡一时，但当地的制造在青铜时代中期结束时停止了。然后在 Tel Burna 又开始了</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 10:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-15/ty-article-magazine/giant-jars-in-small-ancient-town-in-israel-puzzle-archaeologists/0000018f-7b7b-dd4f-ab8f-ffff331a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列独立日，以色列国防军士兵在加沙南部被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-on-israels-independence-day/0000018f-7b63-dd07-adbf-fb73b1500000</link><description>中士。 Ira Yair Gispan，19 岁，来自佩塔提克瓦，是 Amit 和 Talia 的儿子，学习软件工程。他过去的老师形容他有“迷人的微笑”，这让老师很难对他生气</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 09:58:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-on-israels-independence-day/0000018f-7b63-dd07-adbf-fb73b1500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部公布了不到3%的外交护照持有者的姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-ministry-reveals-less-than-3-of-diplomatic-passport-holders/0000018f-7b28-d430-a38f-ffecc5ec0000</link><description>商务部表示，未列出可能危害国家安全、持有人人身安全或对外关系的人员以及未成年人的姓名。亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡 (Yair Netanyahu) 被列入名单，尽管他没有达到入选标准</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 09:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-ministry-reveals-less-than-3-of-diplomatic-passport-holders/0000018f-7b28-d430-a38f-ffecc5ec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列提议：只有在达成协议结束真主党敌对行动后才与黎巴嫩进行边界谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-proposal-border-talks-with-lebanon-only-after-deal-to-end-hezbollah-hostilities/0000018f-78be-d599-ab8f-7cff1cd90000</link><description>贝鲁特渴望尽快就新边界问题展开谈判，但以色列官员宁愿等到战斗结束。根据法律，任何以色列领土的转让都必须进行全民公投——内塔尼亚胡可能很难获得支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 05:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-proposal-border-talks-with-lebanon-only-after-deal-to-end-hezbollah-hostilities/0000018f-78be-d599-ab8f-7cff1cd90000</guid></item></channel></rss>